               <title>PRINCIPAL DISPLAY PANEL</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Clindamycin Phosphate Topical Solution USP, Pledget 1%*</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>*equivalent to 1% (10 mg/mL) clindamycin</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>For Topical Use Only.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Rx Only</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>
